    <div class="bit-60"> 
     <h2>Admitted Students</h2> 
     <p><strong>Congratulations on your admission to Westmont!</strong> With your academic success and desire to pursue a life marked by significance, you’ll thrive at Westmont. As you choose a college—a decision that will shape your future in profound ways—discover how Westmont will prepare you for meaningful work and service wherever God leads you. </p> 
     <p>We seek people like you who desire a strong academic program and want to grow in all areas of your life. Our students not only study the world but care about it and strive to help people however they can: going on a short-term mission; becoming a doctor, teacher or pastor; starting or running a business to provide jobs and a better life; fulfilling the dream that God gives them. They also know how to have fun and enjoy life on campus and in Santa Barbara.</p> 
     <p>Come pursue your passions and discover your calling. Westmont will launch you for life, equipping you with the skills and knowledge you need and connecting you to a strong community of alumni and friends who recognize your worth. </p> 
    </div> 
