     <a id="confirm-offer"></a>
     <h5>Confirm Your Offer of Admission by May 1</h5> 
     <p>Confirm online at <a href="https://secure.westmont.edu/cgi-bin/WebObjects/signup.woa/wa/confirm?type=maycnf" target="_blank">westmont.edu/confirm</a>. Confirmation requires a $500 deposit, preferably by credit card (checks may be submitted, payable to Westmont College). The Housing Application will be at this site and must also be completed with a photo of yourself (passport size). Deposits submitted prior to May 1 are refundable until May 1 upon written request of cancellation of confirmation. Deposits submitted after deadline may be placed on a confirmation Wait List.</p> 
     <div class="app-btn">
      <a href="https://secure.westmont.edu/cgi-bin/WebObjects/signup.woa/wa/confirm?type=maycnf" target="_blank"><img src="images/btn-confirm-admission.png" alt="confirm admission button" width="35%"></a>
     </div> 
